ant;\">Izinkan pengguna memesan rapat di platform dan melakukan panggilan video peer-to-peer atau grup langsung di platform. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tidak perlu menggunakan solusi panggilan video lainnya untuk melakukan rapat.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Cashback: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kami menawarkan pengguna untuk melakukan pembelian dan mengisi ulang persentase tertentu atau jumlah tetap ke dompet mereka setelah melakukan pembelian.&nbsp;</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Bank Soal: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Instruktur dapat menentukan pertanyaan yang berbeda untuk kuis dan menampilkan sejumlah pertanyaan tertentu kepada siswa secara acak atau diurutkan. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Lakukan kuis yang lebih akurat menggunakan fitur ini dengan menghadirkan pertanyaan acak kepada siswa.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kursus Mendatang: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Beri tahu staf platform kami tentang kursus Anda yang akan datang. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Siswa dapat mengikuti kursus yang akan datang dan mereka akan mendapat informasi tentang penerbitan kursus setelah menerbitkan kursus. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Dapatkan adapter awal kursus Anda sebelum memublikasikan kursus.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Cicilan dan Pembayaran Parsial: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Instruktur dapat menjual berbagai materi seperti kursus menggunakan cicilan (Pembayaran Parsial) dan menentukan di muka, langkah pembayaran, dan durasi. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Nonaktifkan platform atau akses kursus untuk cicilan yang terlambat. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistem akan mengirimkan pengingat pembayaran untuk setiap pembayaran.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Host Aman: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Apakah Anda khawatir tentang video dan kursus Anda untuk akses atau pengunduhan dan penyebaran yang tidak diinginkan? </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Instruktur dapat menggunakan fitur ini untuk melindungi konten video Anda dari unduhan yang tidak diinginkan.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pertemuan Jitsi: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Lakukan kelas langsung langsung di Jitsi dan nikmati pengalaman video langsung latensi rendah.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Daftar Tunggu Kursus: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Instruktur dapat mengaktifkan fitur daftar tunggu untuk kursus Anda dan tidak pernah melewatkan calon siswa untuk kursus Anda. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengguna dapat bergabung dengan daftar tunggu kursus Anda saat kapasitas tercapai atau kursus sedang berlangsung. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Beri tahu pengguna daftar tunggu Anda tentang acara mendatang.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Produk Hadiah: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Izinkan pengguna mengirim kursus atau materi lain sebagai hadiah kepada teman mereka segera atau pada tanggal tertentu. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Penerima akan mendapatkan email untuk menerima hadiah.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Multi-mata uang: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Instruktur dapat menjual kursus mereka dalam berbagai mata uang dan mengonversi harga kursus sesuai dengan mata uang yang dipilih. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sediakan gateway pembayaran khusus untuk setiap mata uang. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Fitur ini memungkinkan Anda memperluas bisnis Anda ke seluruh dunia.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Batas Perangkat: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Batasi jumlah sesi masuk untuk pengguna dan hindari berbagi akun antar pengguna. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Hal ini penting untuk menjamin hak instruktur.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Persetujuan Konten Otomatis: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Data yang dibuat instruktur (Kursus, konten, dll) akan diterbitkan secara otomatis tanpa persetujuan admin. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ini akan tersedia untuk beberapa instruktur dengan beberapa aturan</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kursus Pribadi: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Instruktur dapat membuat kursus pribadi yang tidak akan ditampilkan di platform dan admin dapat menambahkan siswa dari panel admin secara manual.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kapasitas Kursus: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Instruktur dapat menentukan kapasitas khusus untuk semua jenis kursus sehingga hanya pengguna dalam jumlah terbatas yang dapat mendaftar di kursus.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span></p>');
INSERT INTO `page_translations` (`id`, `page_id`, `locale`, `title`, `seo_description`, `content`) VALUES
(16, 3, 'it', 'Kemecademy.com La prima accademia immobiliare', 'KEMECADEMY è il primo mercato e piattaforma di corsi in aula online e di persona per collegare istruttori e studenti in tutti i settori immobiliari.', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font class=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY è il primo mercato e piattaforma di corsi in aula online e di persona per collegare istruttori e studenti in tutti i settori immobiliari. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Come tutti i sistemi di Kemedar, questa piattaforma aiuta istruttori e studenti a mettersi in contatto e condividere le conoscenze.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7dcb5d8-7fff-0759-f9b1-a9742e6010c8\" style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY si basa sulle esigenze del settore immobiliare, ricerche avanzate sugli utenti in modo da coprire le tue esigenze in modo efficiente.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">La nostra missione è migliorare le competenze tecniche e professionali delle persone nel settore immobiliare, fornendo una piattaforma di facile utilizzo attraverso la quale chiunque può condividere la propria esperienza dando corsi a pagamento o gratuiti.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY si impegna a beneficiare tutti coloro che lavorano nel settore immobiliare come:</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Tuttofare e professionisti</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Agenti immobiliari</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Sviluppatori immobiliari</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Capi progetto.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Investitori</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Imprenditori immobiliari</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Operatori immobiliari</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Consulenti immobiliari</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Tutor immobiliari</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Giovani e studenti</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Istruttori e tutor professionisti con grande esperienza che amano mettere le loro esperienze a beneficio degli altri. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Molti di loro sono volontari e i loro corsi sono gratuiti per gli studenti dell\'Accademia..</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tutor e istruttori potranno creare corsi video illimitati, lezioni dal vivo, corsi di testo, progetti, quiz, file, ecc. e gli studenti potranno utilizzare il materiale didattico e aumentare il loro livello di abilità.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">PERCHÉ SCEGLIERE KEMECADEMY?</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Dedicato al settore immobiliare</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Integrato con altri sistemi in kemedar.com</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Soluzione completa per online e offline</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- In base alle esigenze del settore immobiliare</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Pacchetti formativi speciali per società immobiliari</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 23pt 0px 15pt; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 20px; padding: 0pt 0pt 7.5pt; color: rgb(23, 19, 71); font-family: main-font-family; border-bottom: 0.75pt solid rgb(212, 212, 212); outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">CARATTERISTICHE</font></span></h2><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">è ricco di molte funzioni utili. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">È possibile visualizzare le funzionalità principali nel seguente elenco:</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Supporto di più contenuti: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY supporta più tipi di contenuto come corsi video, lezioni dal vivo, corsi basati su testo, corsi SCORM e articoli. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Gli istruttori possono selezionare qualsiasi tipo di contenuto desiderino</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Istruzione organizzativa: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY supporta organizzazioni e istituti in modo da poter definire organizzazioni e istituti con studenti e istruttori correlati. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Le organizzazioni possono definire prezzi diversi per i propri studenti.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Riunioni online: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">oltre ai materiali didattici, gli istruttori e le organizzazioni potranno vendere riunioni online e gli studenti potranno prenotare riunioni online, di persona e di gruppo. Questa funzionalità è stata sviluppata pensando ai consulenti immobiliari. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">È un\'ottima funzionalità per consulenti e tutor che vorrebbero vendere la loro consulenza a prezzo orario</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Gateway di pagamento: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">sono supportati 30 gateway per diversi paesi. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Paypal, Stripe, XeedWallet, Razorpay, Paytm, PayU, Paystack, Zarinpal, Paysera, CashU, Robokassa, Mercadopago, Bitpay, Midtrans, Flutterwave, Payfort, Braintree, Mollie, Alipay, Authorize.net, Instamojo, Izipay, Klarna, N- genio, Payku, Paylink, Sslcommerz, Payhere, Toyyibpay, Voguepay, JazzCash, Paysera. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pagamenti offline. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ciò farà sì che l\'istruttore accetti tutti i tipi di pagamenti quando aggiunge il suo corso su Kemecademy</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Supporto Youtube e Vimeo: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli istruttori possono utilizzare i collegamenti video Vimeo e Youtube come parti del corso in modo che possano essere utilizzati come archiviazione video gratuita e sicura.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Accesso tramite social e SMS: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli utenti possono accedere al sistema utilizzando gli account social (Google e Facebook) e sono supportati anche gli SMS e l\'accesso. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Questo renderà la registrazione in pochi secondi per rendere più facile per tutti gli utenti</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistema di abbonamento: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Oltre ai normali acquisti tramite carrello, gli studenti potranno iscriversi ai corsi acquistando diversi piani di abbonamento. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Gli istruttori possono impostare i propri piani di abbonamento per i propri corsi</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Integrazione con Google Calendar: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY è integrato con Google Calendar in modo che gli utenti possano aggiungere tutti gli eventi come sessioni di lezioni dal vivo, riunioni, ecc. al calendario di Google e gli eventi verranno loro ricordati automaticamente in modo che nulla venga perso.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistema di contabilità: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY include un sistema di contabilità integrato che fornisce tracciamento delle transazioni, analisi delle vendite, report avanzati, rimborsi, contabilità manuale, pagamenti, fatture, pagamenti offline, ecc. Gli istruttori saranno tranquilli su tutte le operazioni contabili e si concentreranno solo su la qualità dei loro corsi</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tassi di commissione variabili: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tassi di commissione variabili. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Abbiamo commissioni extra per gli istruttori più attivi e li incoraggiamo.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Quiz e certificazione: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli istruttori possono creare quiz e certificati illimitati e assegnarli ai corsi. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">È possibile definire quiz video e immagini oltre ai quiz testuali. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY include un sistema di certificazione avanzato che ti consente di creare certificati basati su quiz e certificati di completamento del corso.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Badge e sistema di premi: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY ha diversi badge relativi alle azioni dell\'istruttore. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">I badge verranno assegnati automaticamente agli istruttori.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Opzioni di marketing: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">sono disponibili diverse funzionalità di marketing come codici sconto avanzati, promozioni di contenuti, classi in primo piano, sconti sui corsi, banner pubblicitari e modali, newsletter via e-mail, ecc. Per eseguire campagne di marketing. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ciò supporterà gli istruttori nella promozione dei loro corsi anche nei propri canali molto facilmente</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Notifiche: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">le notifiche automatiche verranno inviate dopo ogni processo correlato. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Gli istruttori possono anche inviare notifiche promozionali e personalizzate ai suoi studenti.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistema di supporto: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli studenti potranno entrare in contatto con i docenti all\'interno di un sistema di supporto al corso chiaro e funzionale. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Gli utenti possono anche creare ticket di supporto per l\'amministratore.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Riquadri separati: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY include riquadri separati per docenti, studenti e organizzazioni con diversi tipi di dati.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pagamenti offline: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli utenti potranno addebitare i propri account utilizzando un sistema di pagamento offline e il denaro verrà aggiunto al proprio account dopo l\'approvazione dell\'amministratore.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Opzioni di classe: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">ci sono molte opzioni per ogni classe come capacità della classe, lezioni private, data di inizio della classe, rapporti sulla classe, FAQ, filtri, valutazione, istruttori invitati, ecc. che aiutano gli istruttori a creare materiale didattico professionale per diverse esigenze educative.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sezioni del corso: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli istruttori possono organizzare i materiali del corso in diverse sezioni e capitoli.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Bacheca: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">i docenti possono inviare avvisi personalizzati agli studenti ed esporre gli avvisi in bacheca.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Contenuto multilingue: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">il nostro sistema è multilingue. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Il contenuto verrà caricato in base alla lingua dell\'utente.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Marketing di affiliazione e referral: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">abbiamo il nostro sistema di marketing di affiliazione. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Gli utenti potranno vendere i tuoi corsi e guadagnare. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ciò aumenterà il tuo ritorno in modo molto efficiente</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Corsi SCORM: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">porta l\'esperienza educativa interattiva. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Gli istruttori possono pubblicare corsi realizzati con Adobe Captive, iSpring o qualsiasi altro software.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistema di lezioni dal vivo in-app: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">conduci lezioni dal vivo </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">direttamente su KEMECADEMY </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">con fantastiche funzionalità come chat dal vivo, condivisione dello schermo, ecc. Il tuo studente non verrà reindirizzato a nessun\'altra app di terze parti. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Immagina una schermata di lezione dal vivo sulla tua dashboard KEMECADEMY senza andare da nessuna parte.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kemecoin Points System: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli utenti di KEMECADEMY otterranno punti in base alle loro diverse attività come acquisto, addebito account, pubblicazione di corsi, superamento di un quiz, conseguimento di certificati, commenti, recensioni di corsi, iscrizione alla newsletter, segnalazione di utenti (affiliati), ottenimento di badge, completamento del corso e prenotazione riunioni. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Gli utenti potranno iscriversi ai corsi utilizzando i punti o convertirli in saldo del conto.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tutor Finder: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">consente agli studenti di trovare i migliori istruttori in base a diversi parametri come il livello di tutoraggio, l\'argomento del tutoraggio, il tipo di incontro (online, di persona), l\'ora e il giorno dell\'incontro, la posizione sulla mappa, l\'età e il sesso. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Questa funzione include una bellissima procedura guidata che ottiene informazioni dallo studente e mostrerà le migliori corrispondenze.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Forum e community: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli utenti potranno creare nuovi argomenti in diverse categorie e comunicare insieme su diversi argomenti nel settore immobiliare.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Forum del corso: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">consente agli studenti del corso di porre le loro domande nel forum del corso. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Altri studenti e il docente potranno rispondere alle domande. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Gli studenti possono contrassegnare le domande risolte come \"Risolte\".</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pacchetto di corsi: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli istruttori possono combinare diversi corsi come pacchetto e venderli insieme come pacchetto.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Store &amp; Marketplace: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">questo è un marketplace multi-vendor e una funzione di negozio che consente agli istruttori di vendere prodotti fisici e virtuali. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Come strumenti, libri e materiali necessari con i loro corsi</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Drip Content: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli istruttori possono limitare l\'accesso dello studente ai capitoli e ai file del corso in base a diversi parametri di limitazione come il tempo e il contenuto della sequenza. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">I docenti possono definire di obbligare gli studenti ad accedere alle parti del corso X giorni dopo l\'acquisto del corso o di obbligarli a superare la parte precedente.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Iscrizione manuale: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli insegnanti possono aggiungere manualmente gli studenti a corsi, pacchetti e prodotti.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Assegnazione e compiti a casa:&nbsp;  </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">gli istruttori possono definire compiti diversi per ogni corso con diverse opzioni come voto, scadenza, ecc., e rendere il processo educativo più efficace.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Statistiche e analisi del corso:&nbsp;  </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12