 font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Gerbang pembayaran: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Terdapat 30 gerbang yang disokong untuk negara yang berbeza. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Paypal, Stripe, XeedWallet, Razorpay, Paytm, PayU, Paystack, Zarinpal, Paysera, CashU, Robokassa, Mercadopago, Bitpay, Midtrans, Flutterwave, Payfort, Braintree, Mollie, Alipay, Authorize.net, Instamojo, Izipay, Klarna, N- genius, Payku, Paylink, Sslcommerz, Payhere, Toyyibpay, Voguepay, JazzCash, Paysera. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pembayaran luar talian. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ini akan membuatkan pengajar menerima semua jenis pembayaran apabila dia menambah kursusnya di Kemecademy</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sokongan Youtube &amp; Vimeo: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt