rtical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menghantar notis yang diperibadikan kepada pelajar dan memaparkan notis pada papan kenyataan.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kandungan berbilang bahasa: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistem kami berbilang bahasa. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kandungan akan dimuatkan mengikut bahasa pengguna.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pemasaran Gabungan &amp; Rujukan: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kami mempunyai sistem pemasaran gabungan kami sendiri. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengguna akan dapat menjual kursus anda dan memperoleh pendapatan. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ini akan meningkatkan pulangan anda dengan sangat berkesan</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kursus SCORM: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Bawa pengalaman pendidikan interaktif. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menerbitkan kursus yang dibuat oleh Adobe Captive, iSpring, atau mana-mana perisian lain.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistem Kelas Langsung Dalam Apl: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Jalankan kelas langsung di KEMECADEMY </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">secara langsung </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">dengan ciri hebat seperti sembang langsung, kongsi skrin, dll. Pelajar anda tidak akan diubah hala ke mana-mana apl pihak ketiga yang lain. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Bayangkan skrin kelas langsung pada papan pemuka KEMECADEMY anda tanpa pergi ke mana-mana.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistem Mata Kemecoin: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengguna KEMECADEMY akan mendapat mata mengikut aktiviti berbeza mereka seperti membeli, mengecaj akaun, menerbitkan kursus, lulus kuiz, pencapaian sijil, ulasan, ulasan kursus, menyertai surat berita, merujuk pengguna (Afiliasi), mendapatkan lencana, penyelesaian kursus dan tempahan mesyuarat. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengguna akan dapat mendaftar dalam kursus menggunakan mata atau menukarnya kepada baki akaun.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pencari Tutor: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Membenarkan pelajar mencari pengajar terbaik mengikut parameter berbeza seperti tahap tunjuk ajar, subjek tunjuk ajar, jenis mesyuarat (Dalam Talian, Sendiri), masa dan hari mesyuarat, lokasi pada peta, umur dan jantina. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ciri ini termasuk wizard cantik yang mendapat maklumat daripada pelajar dan akan memaparkan padanan terbaik.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Forum &amp; Komuniti: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengguna akan dapat mencipta topik baharu dalam kategori berbeza dan berkomunikasi bersama tentang subjek berbeza dalam industri hartanah.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Forum Kursus: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Benarkan pelajar kursus bertanya soalan mereka dalam forum kursus. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pelajar lain dan pengajar akan dapat menjawab soalan. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pelajar boleh menandakan soalan yang telah diselesaikan sebagai \"Selesai\".</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pakej Kursus: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menggabungkan beberapa kursus sebagai satu berkas dan menjualnya bersama-sama sebagai satu berkas.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kedai &amp; Pasaran: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ini ialah ciri pasaran dan kedai berbilang vendor yang membenarkan pengajar menjual produk fizikal &amp; maya. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Seperti alat, buku dan bahan yang diperlukan dengan kursus mereka</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kandungan Titis: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menyekat akses pelajar kepada bab dan fail kursus dengan parameter had yang berbeza seperti kandungan masa dan urutan. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menentukan memaksa pelajar mengakses bahagian kursus X hari selepas membeli kursus atau memaksa mereka lulus bahagian sebelumnya.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pendaftaran Manual: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menambah pelajar pada kursus, himpunan dan produk secara manual.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tugasan &amp; Kerja Rumah:&nbsp;  </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menentukan tugasan yang berbeza untuk setiap kursus dengan pilihan yang berbeza seperti gred, tarikh akhir, dll, dan menjadikan proses pendidikan lebih berkesan.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Statistik &amp; Analitis Kursus:&nbsp;  </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh melihat butiran dan statistik kursus dalam persekitaran grafik.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Papan Kenyataan Kursus:&nbsp;  </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menghantar notis yang berbeza kepada pelajar kursus dalam warna yang berbeza.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Panggilan Video Dalam Apl: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Nikmati pengalaman panggilan video dalam apl untuk mengendalikan mesyuarat terus di KEMEKADEMY. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Benarkan pengguna menempah mesyuarat di platform dan menjalankan panggilan video rakan ke rakan atau kumpulan secara terus di platform. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tidak perlu menggunakan penyelesaian panggilan video lain untuk mengendalikan mesyuarat.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pulangan Tunai: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kami menawarkan pengguna untuk membuat pembelian dan mengecas semula peratusan tertentu atau jumlah tetap ke dompet mereka selepas membuat pembelian.&nbsp;</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Bank Soalan: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menentukan soalan yang berbeza untuk kuiz dan memaparkan bilangan soalan tertentu kepada pelajar secara rawak atau disusun. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Jalankan kuiz yang lebih tepat menggunakan ciri ini dengan mengemukakan soalan rawak kepada pelajar.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kursus Akan Datang: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Beritahu stendent platform kami tentang kursus anda yang akan datang. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pelajar boleh mengikuti kursus yang akan datang dan mereka akan mendapat maklumat tentang penerbitan kursus selepas menerbitkan kursus. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Dapatkan penyesuai awal kursus anda sebelum menerbitkan kursus.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ansuran dan Bayaran Separa: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menjual bahan yang berbeza seperti kursus menggunakan ansuran (Bayaran Separa) dan menentukan pendahuluan, langkah pembayaran dan tempoh. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Lumpuhkan akses platform atau kursus untuk ansuran tertunggak. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistem akan menghantar peringatan pembayaran untuk setiap pembayaran.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Hos Selamat: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Adakah anda bimbang tentang video dan kursus anda untuk akses yang tidak diingini atau memuat turun dan menyebarkan? </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menggunakan ciri ini untuk mengekalkan kandungan video anda daripada muat turun yang tidak diingini.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Mesyuarat Jitsi: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Jalankan kelas langsung secara langsung di Jitsi dan nikmati pengalaman video langsung kependaman rendah.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Senarai Tunggu Kursus: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menghidupkan ciri senarai tunggu untuk kursus anda dan jangan sekali-kali terlepas bakal pelajar untuk kursus anda. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengguna boleh menyertai senarai tunggu kursus anda apabila kapasiti dicapai atau kursus sedang berjalan. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Maklumkan kepada pengguna senarai tunggu anda tentang acara akan datang.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Produk Hadiah: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Benarkan pengguna menghantar kursus atau bahan lain sebagai hadiah kepada rakan mereka dengan segera atau pada tarikh tertentu. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Penerima akan mendapat e-mel untuk menerima hadiah.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pelbagai mata wang: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menjual kursus mereka dalam mata wang yang berbeza dan menukar harga kursus mengikut mata wang yang dipilih. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Jadikan gerbang pembayaran khusus tersedia untuk setiap mata wang. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ciri ini membolehkan anda mengembangkan perniagaan anda ke seluruh dunia.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Had Peranti: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Hadkan bilangan sesi log masuk untuk pengguna dan elakkan berkongsi akaun antara pengguna. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ini penting untuk menjamin hak pengajar.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kelulusan Kandungan Auto: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Data yang dibuat oleh pengajar (Kursus, kandungan, dll) akan diterbitkan secara automatik tanpa kelulusan pentadbir. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ini akan tersedia untuk beberapa pengajar dengan beberapa peraturan</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font class=\"VIpgJd-yAWNEb-VIpgJd-fmcmS-sn54Q\" style=\"background-color: rgb(201, 215, 241); box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 170) 2px 2px 4px; position: relative; vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kursus Persendirian: </font></font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font class=\"VIpgJd-yAWNEb-VIpgJd-fmcmS-sn54Q\" style=\"background-color: rgb(201, 215, 241); box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 170) 2px 2px 4px; position: relative; vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh membuat kursus persendirian yang tidak akan dipaparkan pada platform dan pentadbir boleh menambah pelajar kepada mereka daripada panel pentadbir secara manual.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kapasiti Kursus: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pengajar boleh menentukan kapasiti khusus untuk semua jenis kursus jadi hanya bilangan pengguna yang terhad boleh mendaftar dalam kursus.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>');
INSERT INTO `page_translations` (`id`, `page_id`, `locale`, `title`, `seo_description`, `content`) VALUES
(18, 3, 'ru', 'Kemecademy.com Первая академия недвижимости', 'KEMECADEMY — это первая онлайн-площадка и платформа для онлайн-курсов и онлайн-курсов, объединяющая преподавателей и студентов во всех секторах недвижимости.', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY — это первая онлайн-площадка и платформа для онлайн-курсов и онлайн-курсов, объединяющая преподавателей и студентов во всех секторах недвижимости. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Как и все системы Kemedar, эта платформа помогает преподавателям и студентам общаться друг с другом и обмениваться знаниями.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7dcb5d8-7fff-0759-f9b1-a9742e6010c8\" style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY основана на потребностях бизнеса в сфере недвижимости, расширенных исследованиях пользователей, поэтому она эффективно отвечает вашим требованиям.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Наша миссия состоит в том, чтобы повысить технические и профессиональные навыки людей в сфере недвижимости, предоставив простую в использовании платформу, с помощью которой каждый может поделиться своим опытом, проводя платные или бесплатные курсы.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY стремится приносить пользу всем, кто работает в сфере недвижимости, поскольку:</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Разнорабочие и профессионалы</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Риелторы</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Девелоперы недвижимости</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Менеджеры проекта.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Инвесторы</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Предприниматели в сфере недвижимости</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Маркетологи недвижимости</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Консультанты по недвижимости</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Репетиторы по недвижимости</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Молодежь и студенты</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Профессиональные инструкторы и репетиторы с большим опытом, которые любят делиться своим опытом на благо других. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Многие из них являются волонтерами, и их курсы бесплатны для студентов Академии.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Репетиторы и инструкторы смогут создавать неограниченное количество видеокурсов, живых занятий, текстовых курсов, проектов, викторин, файлов и т.&nbsp;д., а студенты смогут использовать учебный материал и повышать уровень своих навыков.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline