gin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Комплексное решение для онлайн и офлайн</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Исходя из потребностей бизнеса в сфере недвижимости</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Специальные учебные пакеты для компаний, занимающихся недвижимостью</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 23pt 0px 15pt; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 20px; padding: 0pt 0pt 7.5pt; color: rgb(23, 19, 71); font-family: main-font-family; border-bottom: 0.75pt solid rgb(212, 212, 212); outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">ФУНКЦИИ</font></span></h2><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">содержит множество полезных функций. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Вы можете просмотреть основные функции в следующем списке:</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Поддержка нескольких типов контента: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY поддерживает несколько типов контента, таких как видеокурсы, живые уроки, текстовые курсы, курсы SCORM и статьи. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели могут выбрать любой тип контента, который они хотели бы</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Организационное образование: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY поддерживает организации и институты, поэтому вы можете определить организации и институты с соответствующими студентами и преподавателями. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Организации могут устанавливать разные цены для своих студентов.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Онлайн-встречи: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">в дополнение к учебным материалам преподаватели и организации смогут продавать онлайн-встречи, а студенты смогут бронировать онлайн-встречи, личные и групповые встречи. Эта функция разработана для консультантов по недвижимости. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Это отличная функция для консультантов и репетиторов, которые хотели бы продавать свои консультации по часовой цене.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Платежные шлюзы: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">поддерживается 30 шлюзов для разных стран. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Paypal, Stripe, XeedWallet, Razorpay, Paytm, PayU, Paystack, Zarinpal, Paysera, CashU, Robokassa, Mercadopago, Bitpay, Midtrans, Flutterwave, Payfort, Braintree, Mollie, Alipay, Authorize.net, Instamojo, Izipay, Klarna, N- гений, Payku, Paylink, Sslcommerz, Payhere, Toyyibpay, Voguepay, JazzCash, Paysera. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Оффлайн платежи. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Это заставит инструктора принимать все виды платежей, когда он добавляет свой курс в Kemecademy.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Поддержка Youtube и Vimeo: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">инструкторы могут использовать видеоссылки на Vimeo и Youtube как части курса, чтобы их можно было использовать в качестве бесплатного и безопасного хранилища видео.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Вход через социальные сети и SMS: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">пользователи могут входить в систему, используя учетные записи социальных сетей (Google и Facebook), также поддерживаются SMS и вход в систему. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Это сделает регистрацию за считанные секунды, чтобы сделать ее легкой для всех пользователей.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Система подписки: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">помимо обычных покупок с использованием корзины, студенты смогут подписаться на курсы, купив различные планы подписки. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели могут устанавливать свои собственные планы подписки на свои курсы.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Интеграция с календарем Google: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY интегрирован с календарем Google, поэтому пользователи смогут добавлять все события, такие как занятия в прямом эфире, встречи и т. д., в календарь Google, и события будут им автоматически напоминаться, поэтому ничего не будет пропущено.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Система учета: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY включает в себя встроенную систему учета, которая обеспечивает отслеживание транзакций, анализ продаж, расширенные отчеты, возвраты, ручной учет, выплаты, счета-фактуры, автономные платежи и т. д. Инструкторы будут спокойны за все бухгалтерские операции и просто сосредоточатся на качество их курсов</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Переменные ставки комиссионных: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Переменные ставки комиссионных. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">У нас есть дополнительные комиссионные ставки для самых активных инструкторов, и мы поощряем их.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Викторина и сертификация. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели могут создавать неограниченное количество викторин и сертификатов и назначать их курсам. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Вы можете определить викторины с видео и изображениями в дополнение к текстовым викторинам. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY включает в себя продвинутую систему сертификации, которая позволяет создавать сертификаты на основе викторин и сертификаты об окончании курса.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Значки и система награждения: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY имеет различные значки, связанные с действиями инструктора. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Бейджи будут присвоены инструкторам автоматически.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Варианты маркетинга: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">для проведения маркетинговых кампаний существует несколько маркетинговых функций, таких как расширенные коды скидок, рекламные акции, рекомендуемые классы, скидки на курсы, рекламные баннеры и модальные окна, информационные бюллетени по электронной почте и т. д. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Это поможет инструкторам очень легко продвигать свои курсы в своих собственных каналах.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Уведомления: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">автоматические уведомления будут отправляться после каждого связанного процесса. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели также могут отправлять рекламные и персонализированные уведомления своим ученикам.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Система поддержки: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">студенты смогут связаться с преподавателями в рамках четкой и функциональной системы поддержки курса. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Пользователи также могут создавать заявки в службу поддержки для администратора.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Отдельные панели: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY включает отдельные панели для преподавателей, студентов и организаций с разными типами данных.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Оффлайн-платежи: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">пользователи смогут взимать плату со своих счетов с помощью системы офлайн-платежей, и деньги будут добавлены к их счету после одобрения администратором.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Варианты класса: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">существует множество параметров для каждого класса, таких как вместимость класса, частные занятия, дата начала занятий, отчеты о занятиях, часто задаваемые вопросы, фильтры, рейтинг, приглашенные преподаватели и т. д., которые помогают преподавателям создавать профессиональные учебные материалы для различных образовательных потребностей.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Разделы курса: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели могут распределять материалы курса по разным разделам и главам.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Доска объявлений: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">преподаватели могут отправлять учащимся персонализированные уведомления и отображать их на доске объявлений.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Многоязычный контент: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Наша система многоязычна. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Контент будет загружен в соответствии с языком пользователя.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Партнерский и реферальный маркетинг: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">у нас есть собственная система партнерского маркетинга. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Пользователи смогут продавать ваши курсы и зарабатывать. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Это очень эффективно увеличит вашу прибыль</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Курсы SCORM: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">интерактивный образовательный опыт. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели могут публиковать курсы, созданные с помощью Adobe Captive, iSpring или любого другого программного обеспечения.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Система онлайн-классов в приложении: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">проводите онлайн-классы </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">напрямую в KEMECADEMY </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">с такими замечательными функциями, как чат в реальном времени, демонстрация экрана и т.&nbsp;д. Ваш ученик не будет перенаправлен в какое-либо другое стороннее приложение. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Представьте себе экран живого занятия на панели инструментов KEMECADEMY, никуда не переходя.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Система баллов Kemecoin: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">пользователи KEMECADEMY будут получать баллы в соответствии с их различными действиями, такими как покупка, пополнение счета, публикация курсов, прохождение викторины, получение сертификата, комментарии, обзоры курсов, присоединение к новостной рассылке, направление пользователей (партнер), получение значков, завершение курса и бронирование встречи. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Пользователи смогут записываться на курсы, используя баллы или конвертируя их в баланс аккаунта.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Поиск репетиторов: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">позволяет учащимся находить лучших инструкторов по различным параметрам, таким как уровень репетиторства, тематика репетиторства, тип встречи (онлайн, лично), время и день встречи, местоположение на карте, возраст и пол. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Эта функция включает в себя красивый мастер, который получает информацию от студента и отображает лучшие совпадения.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Форум и сообщество: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">пользователи смогут создавать новые темы в разных категориях и общаться вместе на разные темы в сфере недвижимости.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Форум курса. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Разрешите учащимся курса задавать свои вопросы на форуме курса. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Другие студенты и преподаватель смогут ответить на вопросы. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Учащиеся могут помечать решенные вопросы как «Решено».</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Пакет курсов: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">преподаватели могут объединить несколько курсов в пакет и продавать их вместе как пакет.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Магазин и торговая площадка: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">это торговая площадка с несколькими поставщиками и функция магазина, которая позволяет инструкторам продавать физические и виртуальные продукты. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Как инструменты, книги и материалы, необходимые для их курсов</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Drip Content: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели могут ограничить доступ учащегося к главам и файлам курса с помощью различных параметров ограничения, таких как время и содержимое последовательности. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели могут указать, что учащиеся должны получить доступ к частям курса через X дней после покупки курса или принудительно пройти предыдущую часть.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Зачисление вручную: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">преподаватели могут вручную добавлять учащихся в курсы, пакеты и продукты.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Задание и домашняя работа:&nbsp;  </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели могут определять разные задания для каждого курса с различными параметрами, такими как оценка, крайний срок и т. д., чтобы сделать процесс обучения более эффективным.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Статистика курса и аналитика:&nbsp;  </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">преподаватели могут просматривать детали курса и статистику в графической среде.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Доска объявлений курса:&nbsp;  </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">преподаватели могут рассылать студентам курса различные уведомления разного цвета.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Видеозвонок в приложении: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">наслаждайтесь видеозвонком в приложении для проведения встреч непосредственно на KEMEKADEMY. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Позвольте пользователям назначать встречи на платформе и проводить одноранговые или групповые видеозвонки прямо на платформе. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Нет необходимости использовать какое-либо другое решение для видеосвязи для проведения совещаний.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Кэшбэк: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">мы предлагаем пользователям совершать покупки и пополнять определенный процент или фиксированную сумму на свои кошельки после совершения покупок.&nbsp;</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Банк вопросов: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">преподаватели могут определять различные вопросы для викторины и отображать определенное количество вопросов для учащихся случайным образом или отсортированными. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Проводите более точные тесты, используя эту функцию, задавая учащимся случайные вопросы.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Предстоящие курсы: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Сообщите участникам нашей платформы о ваших предстоящих курсах. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Студенты могут следить за предстоящими курсами, и они получат информацию о публикации курса после публикации курса. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Получите ранние адаптеры для курса перед публикацией курса.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Рассрочка и частичная оплата: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Инструкторы могут продавать различные материалы, такие как курсы, в рассрочку (частичная оплата) и определять аванс, этапы оплаты и продолжительность. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Отключите доступ к платформе или курсу для просроченных платежей. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Система будет отправлять напоминания о каждом платеже.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Безопасный хост: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">вы беспокоитесь о том, что ваши видео и курсы могут получить несанкционированный доступ или загрузить и распространить? </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели могут использовать эту функцию для защиты вашего видеоконтента от нежелательных загрузок.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Jitsi Meetings: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">проводите живые занятия прямо на Jitsi и наслаждайтесь живым видео с малой задержкой.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Список ожидания курса: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели могут включить функцию списка ожидания для вашего курса и никогда не пропускать потенциальных студентов для ваших курсов. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Пользователи могут присоединиться к вашему списку ожидания курса, когда вместимость будет достигнута или курс уже запущен. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Информируйте пользователей вашего списка ожидания о будущих событиях.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Подарочные продукты. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Разрешите пользователям отправлять курсы или другие материалы в качестве подарков своим друзьям немедленно или в определенную дату. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Получатель получит электронное письмо для получения подарка.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Мультивалютность: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">преподаватели могут продавать свои курсы в разных валютах и ​​конвертировать цены курсов в соответствии с выбранной валютой. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Сделайте определенные платежные шлюзы доступными для каждой валюты. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Эта функция позволит вам расширить свой бизнес по всему миру.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ограничение устройства: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">ограничьте количество сеансов входа в систему для пользователей и избегайте совместного использования учетных записей между пользователями. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Это важно для защиты прав инструкторов.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Автоматическое одобрение контента: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">созданные инструктором данные (курсы, содержание и т.&nbsp;д.) будут опубликованы автоматически без утверждения администратором. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Это будет доступно для некоторых инструкторов с некоторыми правилами</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Частные курсы: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">преподаватели могут создавать частные курсы, которые не будут отображаться на платформе, а администратор может вручную добавлять к ним студентов из панели администратора.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Вместимость курса. </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Преподаватели могут определить конкретную вместимость для всех типов курсов, поэтому на курс может записаться только ограниченное число пользователей.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>');
INSERT INTO `page_translations` (`id`, `page_id`, `locale`, `title`, `seo_description`, `content`) VALUES
(19, 3, 'es', 'Kemecademy.com La primera academia inmobiliaria', 'KEMECADEMI es el primer mercado y plataforma de cursos presenciales y en línea para conectar a instructores y estudiantes en todos los sectores inmobiliarios.', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMI es el primer mercado y plataforma de cursos presenciales y en línea para conectar a instructores y estudiantes en todos los sectores inmobiliarios. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Como todos los sistemas de Kemedar, esta plataforma ayuda a los instructores y estudiantes a ponerse en contacto y compartir conocimientos.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7dcb5d8-7fff-0759-f9b1-a9742e6010c8\" style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY se basa en las necesidades del negocio inmobiliario, investigaciones avanzadas de usuarios para cubrir sus requerimientos de manera eficiente.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Nuestra misión es mejorar las habilidades técnicas y profesionales de las personas en la industria de bienes raíces, proporcionando una plataforma fácil de usar a través de la cual cualquier persona puede compartir su experiencia dando cursos pagos o gratuitos.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY se esfuerza por beneficiar a todos aquellos que trabajan en la industria de bienes raíces como:</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Manitas y Profesionales</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Agentes de Bienes Raices</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Promotores inmobiliarios</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Gerentes de proyecto.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Inversores</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Emprendedores Inmobiliarios</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Comercializadores inmobiliarios</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Consultores Inmobiliarios</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Tutores Inmobiliarios</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Jóvenes y Estudiantes</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Instructores y tutores profesionales con gran experiencia a los que les gusta aportar sus experiencias en beneficio de los demás. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Muchos de ellos son voluntarios y sus cursos son gratuitos para los alumnos de la Academia.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los tutores e instructores podrán crear cursos de video ilimitados, clases en vivo, cursos de texto, proyectos, cuestionarios, archivos, etc., y los estudiantes podrán usar el material educativo y aumentar su nivel de habilidad.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">¿POR QUÉ ELEGIR KEMECADEMI?</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Dedicado a la industria de Bienes Raíces</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Integrado con otros sistemas en kemedar.com</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Solución integral para en línea y fuera de línea</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Basado en las necesidades del negocio inmobiliario</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Paquetes de formación especiales para empresas inmobiliarias</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 23pt 0px 15pt; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 20px; padding: 0pt 0pt 7.5pt; color: rgb(23, 19, 71); font-family: main-font-family; border-bottom: 0.75pt solid rgb(212, 212, 212); outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">CARACTERÍSTICAS</font></span></h2><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">está repleto de muchas funciones útiles. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Puede ver las funciones clave en la siguiente lista:</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Compatibilidad con múltiples contenidos: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY admite múltiples tipos de contenido, como cursos en video, clases en vivo, cursos basados ​​en texto, cursos SCORM y artículos. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los instructores pueden seleccionar cualquier tipo de contenido que deseen</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Educación organizacional: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY apoya a organizaciones e institutos para que pueda definir organizaciones e institutos con estudiantes e instructores relacionados. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Las organizaciones pueden definir diferentes precios para sus propios estudiantes.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Reuniones en línea: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">además de los materiales educativos, los instructores y las organizaciones podrán vender reuniones en línea y los estudiantes podrán reservar reuniones en línea, en persona y grupales. Esta función se desarrolló teniendo en cuenta a los consultores inmobiliarios. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Es una gran característica para consultores y tutores que deseen vender su consulta por precio de hora.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pasarelas de pago: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Hay 30 pasarelas compatibles para diferentes países. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Paypal, Stripe, XeedWallet, Razorpay, Paytm, PayU, Paystack, Zarinpal, Paysera, CashU, Robokassa, Mercadopago, Bitpay, Midtrans, Flutterwave, Payfort, Braintree, Mollie, Alipay, Authorize.net, Instamojo, Izipay, Klarna, N- genio, Payku, Paylink, Sslcommerz, Payhere, Toyyibpay, Voguepay, JazzCash, Paysera. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pagos fuera de línea. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Esto hará que el instructor acepte todo tipo de pagos cuando agregue su curso en Kemecademy</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Compatibilidad con Youtube y Vimeo: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden usar enlaces de video de Vimeo y Youtube como partes del curso para que puedan usarse como almacenamiento de video gratuito y seguro.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Inicio de sesión social y SMS: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los usuarios pueden iniciar sesión en el sistema utilizando cuentas sociales (Google y Facebook), también se admiten SMS e inicio de sesión. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Esto hará que el registro sea en cuestión de segundos para que sea fácil para todos los usuarios.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistema de suscripción: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Además de las compras normales a través del carrito, los alumnos podrán suscribirse a los cursos mediante la compra de diferentes planes de suscripción. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los instructores pueden poner sus propios planes de suscripción para sus cursos.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Integración con el calendario de Google: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMI está integrado con el calendario de Google, por lo que los usuarios podrán agregar todos los eventos, como sesiones de clases en vivo, reuniones, etc., al calendario de Google y se les recordarán los eventos automáticamente para que no se pierda nada.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistema de contabilidad: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY incluye un sistema de contabilidad incorporado que proporciona seguimiento de transacciones, análisis de ventas, informes avanzados, reembolsos, contabilidad manual, pagos, facturas, pagos fuera de línea, etc. Los instructores estarán tranquilos con todas las operaciones contables y solo se concentrarán en la calidad de sus cursos</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tasas de comisión variables: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tasas de comisión variables. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tenemos tarifas de comisión adicionales para la mayoría de los instructores activos y los alentamos.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Cuestionario y certificación: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden crear cuestionarios y certificados ilimitados y asignarlos a los cursos. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Puede definir cuestionarios de video e imagen además de los cuestionarios de texto. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY incluye un sistema de certificación avanzado que le permite crear certificados basados ​​en cuestionarios y certificados de finalización de cursos.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Insignias y sistema de recompensas: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY tiene diferentes insignias relacionadas con las acciones del instructor. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Las insignias se asignarán a los instructores automáticamente.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Opciones de marketing: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">hay varias funciones de marketing, como códigos de descuento avanzados, promociones de contenido, clases destacadas, descuentos en cursos, banners y modales publicitarios, boletines por correo electrónico, etc. para realizar campañas de marketing. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Esto ayudará a los instructores a promocionar sus cursos en sus propios canales con mucha facilidad.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Notificaciones: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Se enviarán notificaciones automáticas después de cada proceso relacionado. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los instructores también pueden enviar notificaciones promocionales y personalizadas a sus alumnos.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistema de soporte: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los estudiantes podrán ponerse en contacto con los instructores dentro de un sistema de soporte del curso claro y funcional. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los usuarios también pueden crear tickets de soporte para el administrador.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Paneles separados: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY incluye paneles separados para instructores, estudiantes y organizaciones con diferentes tipos de datos.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pagos fuera de línea: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los usuarios podrán cargar sus cuentas mediante un sistema de pago fuera de línea y el dinero se agregará a su cuenta después de la aprobación del administrador.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Opciones de clase: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">hay muchas opciones para cada clase, como capacidad de clase, clases privadas, fecha de inicio de clase, informes de clase, preguntas frecuentes, filtros, calificación, instructores invitados, etc. que ayudan a los instructores a crear material educativo profesional para diferentes necesidades educativas.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Secciones del curso: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden organizar los materiales del curso en diferentes secciones y capítulos.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tablón de anuncios: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los profesores pueden enviar avisos personalizados a los estudiantes y mostrarlos en el tablón de anuncios.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Contenido Multi-idioma: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Nuestro sistema es multi-idioma. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">El contenido se cargará según el idioma del usuario.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Marketing de afiliados y referencias: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tenemos nuestro propio sistema de marketing de afiliados. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los usuarios podrán vender sus cursos y ganar. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Esto aumentará su rendimiento de manera muy eficiente.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Cursos SCORM: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">traiga la experiencia educativa interactiva. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los instructores pueden publicar cursos creados por Adobe Captive, iSpring o cualquier otro software.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistema de clases en vivo en la aplicación: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">realice clases en vivo en KEMECADEMY </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">directamente </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">con funciones increíbles como chat en vivo, pantalla compartida, etc. Su estudiante no será redirigido a ninguna otra aplicación de terceros. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Imagina una pantalla de clase en vivo en tu tablero de KEMECADEMI sin ir a ningún lado.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Sistema de puntos de Kemecoin: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los usuarios de KEMECADEMY obtendrán puntos de acuerdo con sus diferentes actividades, como comprar, cargar cuentas, publicar cursos, aprobar un cuestionario, obtener un certificado, comentarios, revisiones de cursos, unirse al boletín informativo, recomendar usuarios (afiliados), obtener insignias, finalización del curso y reserva de reuniones. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los usuarios podrán inscribirse en cursos utilizando puntos o convertirlos en saldo de cuenta.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Buscador de tutores: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">permite a los estudiantes encontrar los mejores instructores de acuerdo con diferentes parámetros, como el nivel de tutoría, el tema de la tutoría, el tipo de reunión (en línea, en persona), la hora y el día de la reunión, la ubicación en el mapa, la edad y el género. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Esta característica incluye un hermoso asistente que obtiene información del estudiante y mostrará las mejores coincidencias.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Foro y comunidad: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los usuarios podrán crear nuevos temas en diferentes categorías y comunicarse juntos sobre diferentes temas en la industria de bienes raíces.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Foro del curso: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Permita que los estudiantes del curso hagan sus preguntas en el foro del curso. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Otros estudiantes y el instructor podrán responder preguntas. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los estudiantes pueden marcar las preguntas resueltas como \"Resueltas\".</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Paquete de cursos: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden combinar varios cursos como un paquete y venderlos juntos como un paquete.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tienda y mercado: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">este es un mercado de múltiples proveedores y una función de tienda que permite a los instructores vender productos físicos y virtuales. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Como herramientas, libros y materiales necesarios con sus cursos.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Contenido por goteo: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden restringir el acceso del estudiante a los capítulos y archivos del curso mediante diferentes parámetros de limitación, como el tiempo y el contenido de la secuencia. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los instructores pueden definir obligar a los estudiantes a acceder a partes del curso X días después de comprar el curso u obligarlos a aprobar la parte anterior.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Inscripción manual: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden agregar estudiantes a cursos, paquetes y productos manualmente.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Asignación y tarea:&nbsp;  </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden definir diferentes tareas para cada curso con diferentes opciones como calificación, fecha límite, etc., y hacer que el proceso educativo sea más efectivo.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Estadísticas y análisis del curso:&nbsp;  </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden ver los detalles y las estadísticas del curso en un entorno gráfico.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Tablón de anuncios del curso:&nbsp;  </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los profesores pueden enviar diferentes avisos a los estudiantes del curso en diferentes colores.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Videollamada en la aplicación: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">disfrute de la experiencia de videollamada en la aplicación para realizar reuniones directamente en KEMEKADEMY. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Permita que los usuarios reserven reuniones en la plataforma y realicen videollamadas entre pares o grupales directamente en la plataforma. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">No es necesario utilizar ninguna otra solución de videollamadas para realizar reuniones.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Cashback: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Ofrecemos a los usuarios realizar compras y recargar un porcentaje específico o cantidad fija a sus billeteras después de realizar las compras.&nbsp;</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Banco de preguntas: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden definir diferentes preguntas para un cuestionario y mostrar un número específico de preguntas a los estudiantes de forma aleatoria u ordenada. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Realice cuestionarios más precisos utilizando esta función presentando preguntas aleatorias a los estudiantes.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Próximos cursos: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">informe a los estudiantes de nuestra plataforma sobre sus próximos cursos. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los estudiantes pueden seguir los próximos cursos y se les informará sobre la publicación del curso después de publicar el curso. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Obtenga los primeros adaptadores de su curso antes de publicar el curso.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Cuotas y pago parcial: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden vender diferentes materiales, como cursos, utilizando la cuota (pago parcial) y definir los pasos de pago por adelantado y la duración. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Inhabilitar acceso a plataforma o curso para cuotas vencidas. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">El sistema enviará recordatorios de pago para cada pago.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Host seguro: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">¿Está preocupado por el acceso no deseado o la descarga y difusión de sus videos y cursos? </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los instructores pueden usar esta función para preservar su contenido de video de descargas no deseadas.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Reuniones de Jitsi: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">realice clases en vivo directamente en Jitsi y disfrute de una experiencia de video en vivo de baja latencia.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Lista de espera del curso: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden activar la función de lista de espera para su curso y nunca perder a estudiantes potenciales para sus cursos. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Los usuarios pueden unirse a la lista de espera de su curso cuando se alcanza la capacidad o el curso está en curso. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Informe a los usuarios de su lista de espera sobre eventos futuros.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Productos de regalo: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">permite a los usuarios enviar cursos u otros materiales como regalos a sus amigos de forma inmediata o en una fecha específica. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">El destinatario recibirá un correo electrónico para recibir el regalo.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Múltiples monedas: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden vender sus cursos en diferentes monedas y convertir los precios de los cursos según la moneda seleccionada. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Pon a disposición pasarelas de pago específicas para cada moneda. </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Esta característica le permite expandir su negocio en todo el mundo.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Límite de dispositivos: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">restrinja la cantidad de sesiones iniciadas para los usuarios y evite compartir cuentas entre usuarios. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Esto es importante para asegurar los derechos de los instructores.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Aprobación automática de contenido: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los datos creados por el instructor (cursos, contenidos, etc.) se publicarán automáticamente sin la aprobación del administrador. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Esto estará disponible para algunos instructores con algunas reglas.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Cursos privados: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden crear cursos privados que no se mostrarán en la plataforma y el administrador puede agregarles estudiantes desde el panel de administración manualmente.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font class=\"VIpgJd-yAWNEb-VIpgJd-fmcmS-sn54Q\" style=\"background-color: rgb(201, 215, 241); box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 170) 2px 2px 4px; position: relative; vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Capacidad del curso: </font></font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font class=\"VIpgJd-yAWNEb-VIpgJd-fmcmS-sn54Q\" style=\"background-color: rgb(201, 215, 241); box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 170) 2px 2px 4px; position: relative; vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">los instructores pueden definir una capacidad específica para todos los tipos de cursos, de modo que solo un número limitado de usuarios pueda inscribirse en el curso.</font></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>');
INSERT INTO `page_translations` (`id`, `page_id`, `locale`, `title`, `seo_description`, `content`) VALUES
(20, 3, 'tr', 'Kemecademy.com İlk Emlak Akademisi', 'KEMECADEMY, tüm emlak sektörlerindeki eğitmenleri ve öğrencileri birbirine bağlayan ilk çevrimiçi ve yüz yüze sınıf kursu pazarı ve platformudur.', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY, tüm emlak sektörlerindeki eğitmenleri ve öğrencileri birbirine bağlayan ilk çevrimiçi ve yüz yüze sınıf kursu pazarı ve platformudur. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Kemedar\'ın tüm sistemlerinde olduğu gibi, bu platform da eğitmenler ve öğrencilerin birbirleriyle iletişim kurmasına ve bilgi paylaşımına yardımcı olur.</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7dcb5d8-7fff-0759-f9b1-a9742e6010c8\" style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY, gayrimenkul iş ihtiyaçlarını, gelişmiş kullanıcı araştırmalarını temel alarak ihtiyaçlarınızı verimli bir şekilde karşılar.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">Misyonumuz, herkesin ücretli veya ücretsiz kurslar vererek uzmanlığını paylaşabileceği kullanımı kolay bir platform sağlayarak emlak sektöründeki kişilerin teknik ve profesyonel becerilerini geliştirmektir.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">KEMECADEMY, gayrimenkul sektöründe çalışan herkese şu şekilde fayda sağlamayı amaçlamaktadır:</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Tamirciler ve Profesyoneller</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Emlakçılar</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Gayrimenkul Geliştiricileri</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Proje yöneticileri.</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Yatırımcılar</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Emlak Girişimcileri</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Emlak Pazarlamacıları</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Emlak Danışmanları</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Emlak Öğretmenleri</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Gençlik ve Öğrenciler</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family