olor: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">NEDEN KEMECADEMY\'Yİ SEÇMELİSİNİZ?</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"outline: none !important;\"><br style=\"outline: none !important;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- Gayrimenkul sektöründe özel</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">- kemedar.com\'daki diğer sistemlerle entegre</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; 