); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">SCORM کورسز: </font></span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">انٹرایکٹو تعلیمی تجربہ لائیں۔ </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">اساتذہ Adobe Captive، iSpring، یا کسی دوسرے سافٹ ویئر کے ذریعے بنائے گئے کورسز کو شائع کر سکتے ہیں۔</font></font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 15pt; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.38; color: rgb(129, 136, 148); font-family: main-font-family; font-size: 16px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\">ان ایپ لائیو کلاس سسٹم: </font></span><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; outline: none !important;\"><f