(6, 8, 'en', '{\"title\":\"Everyone has something to teach. Everyone need something to learn\",\"description\":\"Our mission at Kemecademy is to raise the technical and professional level of all those working in the real estate industry, from craftsmen and technicians to marketers and freelancers. Real estate agents and investors can also take advantage of specialized programs. Kemecademy\'s instructors are all professionals with great experience who love to share their experiences with others. Many of their courses are free of charge. Young people and children can benefit from specialized training programs\",\"hero_background\":\"\\/store\\/1\\/general images\\/hero.jpg\",\"is_video_background\":\"0\"}'),
