(135, 33, 'tr', '{\"image\":\"\\/store\\/1\\/general images\\/club-points.png\",\"title\":\"Kemecoin kazan\\u0131n\",\"description\":\"Kemecademy\'yi kullan\\u0131n ve farkl\\u0131 etkinliklere g\\u00f6re Kemecoin kazan\\u0131n. Jetonlar\\u0131n\\u0131z\\u0131 \\u00fccretsiz \\u00f6d\\u00fcller ve kurslar almak i\\u00e7in kullanabileceksiniz. \\u015eimdi sistemi kullanmaya ba\\u015flay\\u0131n ve paralar\\u0131 toplay\\u0131n!\",\"button1\":{\"title\":\"\\u00d6d\\u00fcller\",\"link\":\"\\/reward-courses\"},\"button2\":{\"title\":\"Kemecoin\'leriniz\",\"link\":\"\\/panel\\/rewards\"}}'),
