(13, 21, 'en', 'Basic 12 principles of landscape gardening', 'Principles of landscape gardening: Landscape gardening is an art that has been around for centuries. It is the process of designing and creating landscapes that are both pleasing to the eye and functional. There are many different aspects to landscape gardening, from choosing the right plants to designing a layout that works well for your space. Whether you are a beginner or a seasoned pro, there is always something new to learn about landscape gardening.', '<p><br></p><div id=\"ez-video-wrap-a54e2ba4c56158f46e2fdd949e344d9a0e9ca244\" class=\"ez-video-wrap\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; text-align: center; clear: both; align-self: stretch; height: auto;\"><div class=\"ez-video-center\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; text-align: left; max-width: 640px;\"><div id=\"ez-video-container-a54e2ba4c56158f46e2fdd949e344d9a0e9ca244\" class=\"ez-video-container ez-float-right\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; z-index: 10000002;\"><div preload=\"metadata\" class=\"video-js ez-vid-placeholder vjs-fluid ez-video-a54e2ba4c56158f46e2fdd949e344d9a0e9ca244-dimensions vjs-controls-enabled vjs-workinghover vjs-v7 vjs-max-quality-selector vjs-vtt-thumbnails vjs-share vjs-videojs-share vjs-vtt-links vjs-has-started vjs-paused vjs-user-inactive\" id=\"ez-video-a54e2ba4c56158f46e2fdd949e344d9a0e9ca244\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"region\" lang=\"en-us\" translate=\"no\" aria-label=\"Video Player\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 640px; height: 0px; padding: 360px 0px 0px; display: block; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(64, 61, 57) !important; position: relative !important; font-size: 10px; line-height: 1; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; word-break: initial; margin: 0px; float: left !important; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"><video id=\"ez-video-a54e2ba4c56158f46e2fdd949e344d9a0e9ca244_html5_api