x;\">Principles of landscape gardening: Landscape gardening is an art that has been around for centuries. It is the process of designing and creating landscapes that are both pleasing to the eye and functional. There are many different aspects to landscape gardening, from choosing the right plants to designing a layout that works well for your space. Whether you are a beginner or a seasoned pro, there is always something new to learn about landscape gardening.</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 3em; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px;\">Landscape gardening is the process of planning and designing outdoor spaces.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px;\">It can involve the creation of gardens, parks, or even entire neighborhoods.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px;\">Landscape architects are responsible for the planning and design of these spaces.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px;\">The goal of landscape gardening is to create beautiful and functional spaces that fit the needs of the client.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px;\">Landscape gardening is a growing field, and there are many opportunities for career growth.</li></ul><div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_48 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-light-blue ez-toc-container-direction\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; direction: ltr; background: rgb(237, 246, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(170, 170, 170); border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 1px 1px; display: table; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 10px 20px 10px 10px; position: relative; width: auto;\"><div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: table; width: 255.281px;\"><p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; display: contents; vertical-align: middle; line-height: 1.45; font-size: 20.4px;\">Table of Contents</p><span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\" style=\"box-sizing: