ortant; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.8-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CPqCupL_-f4CFU_b1QodqYUFcA\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.H_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Landscaping rake</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​Landscaping rakes are much more robust than typical gardening rakes. These generally consist of a long, robust wooden handle and a wide head. The rake head has thick, tubular \'tines\' or teeth which can be used to rake out beds of loose soil and aggregates. This landscaping rake below&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Faithfull-Aluminium-Landscape-Rake-Handle/dp/B0001IWR5W?cv_ct_cx=landscaping+rake&amp;dchild=1&amp;keywords=landscaping+rake&amp;pd_rd_i=B0001IWR5W&amp;pd_rd_r=ed9feb97-028b-45ef-abf8-ddd222f413ee&amp;pd_rd_w=cW4bp&amp;pd_rd_wg=QknBt&amp;pf_rd_p=1d13bff8-47cf-4a87-a6dc-3d450fd9093d&amp;pf_rd_r=2KRYQ4QR0WYMX32KDQPX&amp;qid=1628939779&amp;sr=1-1-439ac954-ad46-4ba0-bd86-480f8aab80ed&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=8b97d64654b9feacdd48ed9212ef7afc&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">is available&nbsp;on amazon here.&nbsp;</a><br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"332377220595049447\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Faithfull-Aluminium-Landscape-Rake-Handle/dp/B0001IWR5W?cv_ct_cx=landscaping+rake&amp;dchild=1&amp;keywords=landscaping+rake&amp;pd_rd_i=B0001IWR5W&amp;pd_rd_r=ed9feb97-028b-45ef-abf8-ddd222f413ee&amp;pd_rd_w=cW4bp&amp;pd_rd_wg=QknBt&amp;pf_rd_p=1d13bff8-47cf-4a87-a6dc-3d450fd9093d&amp;pf_rd_r=2KRYQ4QR0WYMX32KDQPX&amp;qid=1628939779&amp;sr=1-1-439ac954-ad46-4ba0-bd86-480f8aab80ed&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=082aa48d507fe7453e7008de7759d70a&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B0001IWR5W&amp;Format=_SL500_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B0001IWR5W\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"6\">Setting out</font></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​<br>​Setting out is an essential part of landscaping. More often than not a landscaper is either working to a garden design drawing or specific specifications. When dealing with materials simply digging an extra 2cm depth over a large area can lead to significant quantities.<br><br>When considering modern waste and material costs poor setting out can break a projects budget. Therefore setting out precise measurements and quantifying levels is an essential landscaping skill.<br><br>​In order for a landscaper to be effective in setting out he will also require some tools. These essential setting out landscaping tools have been listed and described below.&nbsp;</font></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc-container-5\" class=\"mmt-container-flight\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-direction: row;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.9\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.9-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.9-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.9-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CMSL-pL_-f4CFWACBgAd6UIMIQ\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.I_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.10\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.10-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.10-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.10-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CJDw-ZL_-f4CFVmz1QodZIYKHQ\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.J_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">String line</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">String lines are one of the only true definitive ways of creating a physical line from one feature to another.<br><br>This makes them invaluable for building straight edges and landscape installations. Being one of the most crucial landscaping tools they are also one of the most simplest. These generally consist of a flexible cord of string with a metal pin at each end.<br><br>​The pins can be used to hammer each pin securely into surfaces to anchor them. Setting up string lines correctly can take some practice! It is important to keep testing your strings position as you work so you don’t accidently drift off target.&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Spear-Jackson-Line-Pins-10505Z/dp/B002TYZOTM?dchild=1&amp;keywords=string+line+building&amp;qid=1628940039&amp;sr=8-20&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=24707be882f2c69d0999eeb630b5318a&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">To access the string line and pins below find them on Amazon here.&nbsp;</a></font></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"317480367254813182\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Spear-Jackson-Line-Pins-10505Z/dp/B002TYZOTM?dchild=1&amp;keywords=string+line+building&amp;qid=1628940039&amp;sr=8-20&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=8a31334b4b05ace6ef093f67a69d808f&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B002TYZOTM&amp;Format=_SL400_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B002TYZOTM\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Long spirit levels</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">Long levels the kind of which bricklayers use are extremely effective landscaping tools. These enable you to check levels and falls spanning wider distances which is crucial in landscaping.<br><br>​These levels are commonly used for ‘pegging out’ particularly when excavating patios. Pegs are driven in to the ‘finished height’ of a surface. A long spirit level is then used to drive more pegs into the ground at the same level. This enables you to accurately excavate large areas to the same level. This professional Stanley&nbsp;level can be found&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Stanley-143558-FatMax-I-Beam-Magnetic/dp/B004S44FQE?dchild=1&amp;keywords=long+spirit+level&amp;qid=1628940298&amp;sr=8-13&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=4e20273eeff625368d28d536d397d324&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">on Amazon here.</a></font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"935098747676452139\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Stanley-143558-FatMax-I-Beam-Magnetic/dp/B004S44FQE?dchild=1&amp;keywords=long+spirit+level&amp;qid=1628940298&amp;sr=8-13&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=439cb9a5f05712cfc7eeba34d4f18ec2&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B004S44FQE&amp;Format=_SL500_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B004S44FQE\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc-container-6\" class=\"mmt-container-flight\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-direction: row;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.11\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.11-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.11-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-cont