quares which enable you to accurately set out right angles. These are perfect for making sure new paths and borders are 90 degrees from the building. Typically landscaping set squares are made from thin metal slats with rivets. This means they can be folded out and locked into a triangle, then folded back for easy storage. The one below can be&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Folding-Aluminium-Construction-Flooring-Builders/dp/B07NSSQH8S?dchild=1&amp;keywords=large+set+square&amp;qid=1628940480&amp;sr=8-3-spons&amp;psc=1&amp;spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUFEWEFRQ05RVU5XWUsmZW5jcnlwdGVkSWQ9QTA2MDcwMjUyRU5PTEVMMEdLMFVYJmVuY3J5cHRlZEFkSWQ9QTAxMzMwNzAxU0k5ODU3VVRKWk1PJndpZGdldE5hbWU9c3BfYXRmJmFjdGlvbj1jbGlja1JlZGlyZWN0JmRvTm90TG9nQ2xpY2s9dHJ1ZQ%3D%3D&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=2f8d4f91f4b4e29d7d84c3e290135b48&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">found on Amazon here.</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"272577291175516336\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Folding-Aluminium-Construction-Flooring-Builders/dp/B07NSSQH8S?dchild=1&amp;keywords=large+set+square&amp;qid=1628940480&amp;sr=8-3-spons&amp;psc=1&amp;spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUFEWEFRQ05RVU5XWUsmZW5jcnlwdGVkSWQ9QTA2MDcwMjUyRU5PTEVMMEdLMFVYJmVuY3J5cHRlZEFkSWQ9QTAxMzMwNzAxU0k5ODU3VVRKWk1PJndpZGdldE5hbWU9c3BfYXRmJmFjdGlvbj1jbGlja1JlZGlyZWN0JmRvTm90TG9nQ2xpY2s9dHJ1ZQ%3D%3D&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=e660b4c56b57b9656ff30c8cd7a70029&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B07NSSQH8S&amp;Format=_