 extremely durable and hard wearing generally requiring concrete foundations and cement based mortars. Consequently masonry work requires a whole new array of specific skills and landscaping tools. These have been listed and described below.&nbsp;<br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div class=\"wsite-image wsite-image-border-none\" style=\"position: relative; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\"><img src=\"https://www.buckinghamshirelandscapegardeners.com/uploads/1/9/7/4/19746843/imag0226_orig.jpg\" alt=\"Patio laying\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; max-width: 100%; width: auto; border-width: 0px !important;\"></a><div style=\"font-size: 12.6px;\"></div></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc-container-8\" class=\"mmt-container-flight\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-direction: row;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.15\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.15-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.15-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.15-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CMjj-ZL_-f4CFdADBgAdqxoMmQ\"><div id=