mportant;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc-container-9\" class=\"mmt-container-flight\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-direction: row;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.17\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.17-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.17-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.17-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CM2i-pL_-f4CFQTxUQodJDEA6g\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.Q_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.18\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.18-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.18-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.18-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CPGJ-pL_-f4CFcj3UQodZBUIDQ\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.R_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Rubber mallet</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​<br>Sometimes humorously referred to in the trade as a ‘persuader’ rubber mallets are ideal tampers. These are commonly used to tamp down paving onto wet mortar without cracking the pavers. Rubber mallets can also be used to move other heavy materials on mortar without causing surface trauma. The Maxpower rubber mallet below is a popular choice and is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/MAXPOWER-Rubber-Hickory-Installation-24-Ounce/dp/B00HE982FU?dchild=1&amp;keywords=rubber+mallet&amp;qid=1629021702&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-7-spons&amp;psc=1&amp;spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUExMDdPVTVBWjNYNjNGJmVuY3J5cHRlZElkPUEwMjY5MTYwS1UzRlpOTDJZQTdYJmVuY3J5cHRlZEFkSWQ9QTA3OTk0OTYyMDBMTEJKR0MzWUk2JndpZGdldE5hbWU9c3BfbXRmJmFjdGlvbj1jbGlja1JlZGlyZWN0JmRvTm90TG9nQ2xpY2s9dHJ1ZQ%3D%3D&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=de3b0d68a6a0a9b12dfad9a3ac404a8b&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">available on Amazon.&nbsp;</a><br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"975196172220423128\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/MAXPOWER-Rubber-Hickory-Installation-24-Ounce/dp/B00HE982FU?dchild=1&amp;keywords=rubber+mallet&amp;qid=1629021702&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-7-spons&amp;psc=1&amp;spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUExMDdPVTVBWjNYNjNGJmVuY3J5cHRlZElkPUEwMjY5MTYwS1UzRlpOTDJZQTdYJmVuY3J5cHRlZEFkSWQ9QTA3OTk0OTYyMDBMTEJKR0MzWUk2JndpZGdldE5hbWU9c3BfbXRmJmFjdGlvbj1jbGlja1JlZGlyZWN0JmRvTm90TG9nQ2xpY2s9dHJ1ZQ%3D%3D&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=6fd4ad803394cbc4667738708911d539&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B00HE982FU&amp;Format=_SL500_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B00HE982FU\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Spirit level</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">Spirit levels come in a variety of sizes and lengths. As discussed earlier spirit levels comprise of a straight edge with a levelling gauge. The gauge consists of a cavity filled with fluid and a single air bubble. The transparent compartment which encases the fluid has two parallel lines on the casing.<br>​<br>When the straight edge of the unit is held completely level the bubble sits perfectly within the two lines. Spirit levels also have a vertical gauge which levels the vertical plane or plumb. Spirit levels are essential landscaping tools and crucial for a wide range of external installations. Below is a classic example of a popular brand of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Stabila-70-2-90-Level-90cm-70236/dp/B0001P0TKU?dchild=1&amp;keywords=spirit+level&amp;qid=1629022132&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-9&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=43651ed889eba77fc6b0a4ff93383168&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">spirit level, Stabila.</a><br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"548571059673693219\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Stabila-70-2-90-Level-90cm-70236/dp/B0001P0TKU?dchild=1&amp;keywords=spirit+level&amp;qid=1629022132&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-9&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=ea150c579499a16dc2044c7555be3ef2&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B0001P0TKU&amp;Format=_SL500_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B0001P0TKU\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc-container-10\" class=\"mmt-container-flight\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-direction: row;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.19\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.19-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.19-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.19-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CNb2-ZL_-f4CFZgEBgAdN-IIUw\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.S_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.20\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.20-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.20-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.20-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CL_s-ZL_-f4CFceN1QodS5IBWA\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.T_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Club hammer</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​<br>​Club hammers are short, heavy, hammers with a large striking head. They allow for short, powerful blows to masonry and other robust, heavy materials. Club hammers however are traditionally used in partnership with bolsters. This stanley club hammer is available&nbsp;on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Stanley-156001-Anti-Vibe-Lump-Hammer/dp/B000X2B4UK?dchild=1&amp;keywords=club+hammer&amp;qid=1629022909&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-4&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=de0cc698a674db8ade1727dbe83ad6c2&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">Amazon here.</a><br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div i