de. These are traditionally used to cut bricks and blocks neatly in half. They are also effective at prizing open cracks, separating attached materials and chipping off protruding nuggets of cement. We have linked to this&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Draper-Redline-68603-Brick-Bolster/dp/B011KJHGRO?dchild=1&amp;keywords=bolster&amp;qid=1629023278&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-3&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=8cbda3cb0617a651856e891dd3ee8ce4&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">popular bolster brand below.&nbsp;</a><br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"534464893400649951\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Draper-Redline-68603-Brick-Bolster/dp/B011KJHGRO?dchild=1&amp;keywords=bolster&amp;qid=1629023278&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-3&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=43a8d1dca8dea12fef8a14895579fee3&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B011KJHGRO&amp;Format=_SL400_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B011KJHGRO\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: j