title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"6\">Timber work</font><br></h2><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">Timber is an extremely versatile material which is both strong and flexible. Coming in a wide variety densities, grades and finishes it is no wonder it’s a popular landscaping material.<br><br>​From raised planters, pergolas, decking, fencing to edging it has many garden uses. Consequently there are many landscaping tools which are specifically required for timber work. These range from heavy duty cutting tools to fixing and joining.&nbsp;</font></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Circular saw</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​Circular saws are hand held electrical cutters suitable for cutting a wide range of timber. These small but powerful saws allow you cut timber quickly and efficiently. These are perfect for landscaping projects such as decking and custom built pergolas.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Makita-HS7601J-Circular-MakPac-Carry/dp/B012CKRAYY?crid=7A5N2G8V93CL&amp;dchild=1&amp;keywords=circular+saw&amp;qid=1629023497&amp;s=diy&amp;sprefix=circular%2Cdiy%2C198&amp;sr=1-4&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=b1d42d2d3e90f65d6a61247b2ba000b6&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">This Makita circular saw</a>&nbsp;is a very popular saw for general timber work.<br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"385225731229761889\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Makita-HS7601J-Circular-MakPac-Carry/dp/B012CKRAYY?crid=7A5N2G8V93CL&amp;dchild=1&amp;keywords=circular+saw&amp;qid=1629023497&amp;s=diy&amp;sprefix=circular%2Cdiy%2C198&amp;sr=1-4&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=6f746ee3b2273404d97a2f3f1c79a83a&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B012CKRAYY&amp;Format=_SL400_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B012CKRAYY\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; marg