" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Chainsaw</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">Chainsaws are not the most common landscaping tools but most landscapers do own one. This is due to the fact they are unmatched when it comes to cutting very thick timbers. For example timber sleepers are more than a handful for most electric saws.<br><br>​In order to achieve a clean, right, angle cut however they are best used with a \'Handy saw horse\'. Chain saws are also good at cutting logs and creating rustic sculpture. These are&nbsp; however are extremely dangerous and should only be operated by trained professionals.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Stihl-MS181-14-Inch-Chain-Saw/dp/B009R4FAX2?crid=68LRFTXYK53T&amp;dchild=1&amp;keywords=chainsaw+stihl&amp;qid=1629031599&amp;sprefix=chainsaw+st%2Caps%2C179&amp;sr=8-6&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=02bcdcb8c7f843104d82e995ffc9a898&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">Stihl chainsaws</a>&nbsp;like the one below are the professionals chainsaw of choice.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"404061155362227562\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Stihl-MS181-14-Inch-Chain-Saw/dp/B009R4FAX2?crid=449F6PC5GTF3&amp;dchild=1&amp;keywords=stihl+chainsaw&amp;qid=1629031296&amp;sprefix=stil+chainsaw%2Cdiy%2C184&amp;sr=8-5&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=86304d04d8de7301e8f148fd3f758c78&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B009R4FAX2&amp;Format=_SL500_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B009R4FAX2\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Cordless drill</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​Cordless drills are essential for the quick drilling and fixing of timber in those awkward spaces. These are effective at fixing joist work especially on high up pergolas or awkward decking joists. Every landscaper is pretty much guaranteed to own one and can be used for a variety of other projects. The Makita combi cordless drill below is very popular with landscapers and available&nbsp;on<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Makita-DLX2131TJ-Li-ion-DHP482-DTD152/dp/B083Y43L5S?dchild=1&amp;keywords=makita+drill&amp;qid=1629031698&amp;sr=8-5&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=db71dd79f38737f08097d9d42ecf334b&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">Amazon here.</a></font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"366336095532516874\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Makita-DLX2131TJ-Li-ion-DHP482-DTD152/dp/B083Y43L5S?crid=3CRAAK987QQ0G&amp;dchild=1&amp;keywords=makita+drill&amp;qid=1629031399&amp;sprefix=makita+drill%2Caps%2C185&amp;sr=8-5&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=68ef0081529c6bb5b1d2c83232eb5d8c&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B083Y43L5S&amp;Format=_SL400_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B083Y43L5S\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc-container-14\" class=\"mmt-container-flight\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-direction: row;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.27\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.27-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.27-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.27-ad\"></div></div></div></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.28\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.28-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.28-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.28-ad\"></div></div></div></div></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Extension cable</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​Not really thought of as a landscaping tool but every landscaper would be lost without a long and robust extension cable. These reels generally host 4 standard plug sockets and provide you with electrical power even in the largest of gardens.&nbsp;</font></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"191421158535828593\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Masterplug-OLU50134SL-PX-Pro-XT-Length-Medium/dp/B014L2OOYK?dchild=1&amp;keywords=50m+extension+cable&amp;qid=1629032027&amp;sr=8-8&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=1416580e6c43378d1cea90c843c0f28f&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B014L2OOYK&amp;Format=_SL400_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B014L2OOYK\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"6\">Landscaping power tools&nbsp;</font></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​<br>​Landscaping requires physical effort but for most projects man power alone is simply not enough. Some of the most effective landscaping tools are power tools, some of which you simply can’t do without. From demolition to mixing mortar to cutting and compaction I have listed the top landscaping power tools below.&nbsp;</font></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc-container-15\" class=\"mmt-container-flight\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-direction: row;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.29\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.29-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.29-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.29-ad\"></div></div></div></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.30\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.30-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.30-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.30-ad\"></div></div></div></div></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Breakers</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;​Breakers come in a variety of sizes and grades and are usually either electric or hydraulic. Most of the time a landscaper doesn’t really need to own a heavy duty breaker. If encountering strong concrete more than 100mm it is probably best to hire a larger machine. Most of the time smaller, hand held breakers are good value and are enough for most landscaping projects. This hand held VonHaus breaker is a good example and is available&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/VonHaus-Electric-Breaker-Demolition-Concrete/dp/B06XFHR6S5?dchild=1&amp;keywords=breaker&amp;qid=1629032151&amp;sr=8-6&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=ed0df4e5be3658d4c374b6e0b4affb63&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">on Amazon here.</a><br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"107934110763807917\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/VonHaus-Electric-Breaker-Demolition-Concrete/dp/B06XFHR6S5?dchild=1&amp;keywords=breaker&amp;qid=1629032151&amp;sr=8-6&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=822fd82ae3646d6d74b51c62a19c4eaf&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B06XFHR6S5&amp;Format=_SL500_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B06XFHR6S5\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Grinders</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​<br>​Grinders come in three common sizes; 12inch, 9inch and 4.5inch. The smallest of these are less effective for landscaping in general but good for chasing out pointing. Both 9inch and 12inch are more typically used and fitted with a diamond blade. These are perfect for cutting paving and to create a clean edge to stone or concrete surfaces.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Makita-GA9020KD-Angle-Grinder-Diamond/dp/B003SODS6S?&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=c63acf63a43cdec452e7af037f4e5121&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">This 9 inch Makita grinder</a>&nbsp;is a very effective all-round landscaping power tool.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"802757777105656060\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Makita-GA9020KD-Angle-Grinder-Diamond/dp/B003SODS6S?&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=567315854b1596c52455db7ef5165327&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B003SODS6S&amp;Format=_SL300_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B003SODS6S\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc-container-16\" class=\"mmt-container-flight\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-direction: row;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.31\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.31-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.31-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.31-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CMjd-pL_-f4CFc4LBgAdx1YOUQ\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.__0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.32\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.32-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.32-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.32-ad\"></div></div></div></div></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Power drills</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​Power drills provide just that extra clout that cordless drills lack. SDS drills in particular are more suitable for heavy duty landscaping tasks. They have a more robust attachment grip between the drills shaft and the working attachments. This makes them less likely to slip during high, velocity tasks. These also have a hammer and chisel setting providing a wide range of uses. This JCB power drill is a popular choice and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B08WKKNJHR?psc=1&amp;pd_rd_i=B08WKKNJHR&amp;pd_rd_w=lxkmp&amp;pf_rd_p=62ac3676-b530-493d-9fe9-14410b1870a2&amp;pd_rd_wg=CzKZ6&amp;pf_rd_r=BPSF3ZNTDFJXP98CYYC8&amp;pd_rd_r=8a415992-c9a7-4d5b-9e4d-89a995de536e&amp;spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUEzVTNPUFpRU1RSTTNYJmVuY3J5cHRlZElkPUEwNjg3Mzg1M0hZQk1FT0pRMkVVViZlbmNyeXB0ZWRBZElkPUEwODUyNzA3MVRON0pSSDBSMUVQNCZ3aWRnZXROYW1lPXNwX2RldGFpbCZhY3Rpb249Y2xpY2tSZWRpcmVjdCZkb05vdExvZ0NsaWNrPXRydWU%3D&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=89901820dfbd8d39daed98036d44f5ec&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">available&nbsp;here</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>​</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"109159339814606623\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B08WKKNJHR?psc=1&amp;pd_rd_i=B08WKKNJHR&amp;pd_rd_w=lxkmp&amp;pf_rd_p=62ac3676-b530-493d-9fe9-14410b1870a2&amp;pd_rd_wg=CzKZ6&amp;pf_rd_r=BPSF3ZNTDFJXP98CYYC8&amp;pd_rd_r=8a415992-c9a7-4d5b-9e4d-89a995de536e&amp;spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUEzVTNPUFpRU1RSTTNYJmVuY3J5cHRlZElkPUEwNjg3Mzg1M0hZQk1FT0pRMkVVViZlbmNyeXB0ZWRBZElkPUEwODUyNzA3MVRON0pSSDBSMUVQNCZ3aWRnZXROYW1lPXNwX2RldGFpbCZhY3Rpb249Y2xpY2tSZWRpcmVjdCZkb05vdExvZ0NsaWNrPXRydWU%3D&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=e4fd75001b494468aaa9741fae135e62&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B08WKKNJHR&amp;Format=_SL400_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B08WKKNJHR\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Pressure washers</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​Not only are pressure washers effective at revamping old surfaces they are perfect landscaping tools. This is mainly for the task of cleaning a project after completion. Typically wheel barrows and footfall during bad weather can compact dirt and materials into surfaces.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Pressure-Paxcess-Electric-Portable-Driveway/dp/B08TQ6F2PK?dchild=1&amp;keywords=pressure+washers&amp;qid=1629033157&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-6&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=39d24c07f1ebdd69272a70304076611e&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">Pressure washers</a>&nbsp;enable you to clean a project thoroughly before you leave which always leads to happy clients.&nbsp;<br>​&nbsp;</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"261717290370905913\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Pressure-Paxcess-Electric-Portable-Driveway/dp/B08TQ6F2PK?dchild=1&amp;keywords=pressure+washers&amp;qid=1629033157&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-6&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=801099ad99e098c7f1d2726840772ec1&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B08TQ6F2PK&amp;Format=_SL400_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B08TQ6F2PK\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc-container-17\" class=\"mmt-container-flight\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-direction: row;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.33\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.33-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.33-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.33-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CIiZ-5L_-f4CFdYHBgAd_1sNbQ\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.a_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.34\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.34-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.34-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.34-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CJqz-5L_-f4CFQYWBgAdy0oCaA\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.b_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Compacter plate</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​<br>​Compactor plates are heavy machines which vibrate at a high velocity. This makes them perfect for compacting base aggregates and in particular MOT Type 1. Commonly known as \'whackers\' these landscaping tools utilise an action called vibro compaction. This is where angular particles vibrate together so violently they almost bind together in dense compaction. These are most commonly used in surfacing projects such as paving. This Hyundai&nbsp;petrol compaction plate is perfect for compacting sub bases for a multitude of surfaces and is available&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Hyundai-HYCP6570-Petrol-Compactor-Wacker/dp/B01MG56H3C?dchild=1&amp;keywords=compactor+plate&amp;qid=1629033346&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-16&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=1d807635480b5ec80306823598e32ca7&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">on Amazon here.</a></font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"607448591961130863\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Hyundai-HYCP6570-Petrol-Compactor-Wacker/dp/B01MG56H3C?dchild=1&amp;keywords=compactor+plate&amp;qid=1629033346&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-16&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=e70dfe8a66f0357199434b744534141c&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B01MG56H3C&amp;Format=_SL400_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B01MG56H3C\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Cement mixer</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​<br>​Cement mixers are quite simply a staple landscaping tool with very few professional projects not requiring one. For this reason it is unlikely a landscaper would not own their own. Cement mixers are particularly valued for landscapers who undertake a lot of brickwork and paving.&nbsp; You can purchase either electric or gasoline cement mixers to suit your preference. This electric portable cement mixer is available on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Portable-Concrete-Electric-Adjustment-Building/dp/B07TCFX66X?dchild=1&amp;keywords=cement+mixer&amp;qid=1629034482&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-9&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=3827cbce1101c3f4257d595fb128149e&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">Amazon here.&nbsp;</a><br>​&nbsp;</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"855540917822118838\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Portable-Concrete-Electric-Adjustment-Building/dp/B07TCFX66X?dchild=1&amp;keywords=cement+mixer&amp;qid=1629034482&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-9&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=d7c8d84e071a56eb2538f355f9d49510&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B07TCFX66X&amp;Format=_SL400%20&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B07TCFX66X\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc-container-18\" class=\"mmt-container-flight\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-direction: row;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.35\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.35-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.35-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.35-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CIzBpaT_-f4CFTcOBgAddusKPg\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.c_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.36\" class=\"mmt-primary mmt-flight\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px !important; flex: 1 1 auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.36-cls2\" style=\"display: table; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.36-cls1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgba(233, 233, 233, 0.5); padding: 10px; min-width: 320px !important; min-height: 250px !important; box-sizing: content-box !important;\"><div id=\"mmt-biacdsid-f2ic-jitb-kmil-ictoamttthtc.36-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CN_YvqT_-f4CFQq91QodJXwJFg\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/20842576,22874681548/JF002M/JF002M-DDL.d_0__container__\" style=\"border: 0pt none; width: 300px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Generator</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><br><font size=\"4\">​​Generators can be vital landscaping tools for landscapers who regularly find themselves off grid. This is commonly the case on larger, commercial, landscaping projects or in rural locations. Generators can be a great way to move power around with you on large sites with no threat of severing cables. Generators are always a good thing to have just in case there is a prolonged power cut. This portable, petrol, Parker brand generator is great for working off grid and is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/2-8-2-8KW-6-5HP-Petrol-Generator/dp/B00FFHJ6D0?dchild=1&amp;keywords=petrol+generator&amp;qid=1629034798&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-3&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=dfcb0bd2fcbc850711048980a88a10b4&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">available&nbsp;here.&nbsp;</a></font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div id=\"274158158107245521\" align=\"center\" class=\"wcustomhtml\" style=\"width: 740px; overflow-y: hidden;\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/2-8-2-8KW-6-5HP-Petrol-Generator/dp/B00FFHJ6D0?dchild=1&amp;keywords=petrol+generator&amp;qid=1629034798&amp;s=diy&amp;sr=1-3&amp;linkCode=li3&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=a6e433d433ffd5dc83b4a6ada46a29b3&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_il\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166); text-decoration-line: underline;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://ws-eu.amazon-adsystem.com/widgets/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B00FFHJ6D0&amp;Format=_SL400_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=GB&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><img src=\"https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=320d-21&amp;language=en_GB&amp;l=li3&amp;o=2&amp;a=B00FFHJ6D0\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important;\"></div></div><div class=\"wsite-spacer\" style=\"color: rgb(82, 82, 82); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; height: 50px;\"></div><h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 30px !important; font-weight: 400 !important; font-family: Lato !important; color: rgb(80, 141, 36) !important;\"><font size=\"5\">Tiller&nbsp;</font><br></h2><div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: auto; border: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px !important; line-height: 23px !important; font-family: Arial !important; color: rgb(81, 81, 81) !important;\"><font size=\"4\">​It is very common for landscapers to prepare planting beds or areas to be turfed or seeded. One of the best ways to work the soil to a loose and crumbly texture is to use a tiller. These powerful machines have rotating blades which cut deeply and turn the ground. This breaks up clods of soil and makes it easy to work to a fine tilth. These come in a range of sizes but the larger, more powerful gasoline machines are even more effective. This<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B08BX4LYFG?psc=1&amp;pd_rd_i=B08BX4LYFG&amp;pd_rd_w=IqmOK&amp;pf_rd_p=62ac3676-b530-493d-9fe9-14410b1870a2&amp;pd_rd_wg=51ik1&amp;pf_rd_r=NS7RF3K0MSH6VMR46X7Z&amp;pd_rd_r=19f7c5e5-3ac6-43a4-8c9f-e0fea7d33895&amp;spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUFYUVJUSUMwRVdMTDUmZW5jcnlwdGVkSWQ9QTA0NDUwMjUyNzBXWEtQS0FYU0xYJmVuY3J5cHRlZEFkSWQ9QTA5MzY0ODA2U1g1R080SjhOR0Mmd2lkZ2V0TmFtZT1zcF9kZXRhaWwmYWN0aW9uPWNsaWNrUmVkaXJlY3QmZG9Ob3RMb2dDbGljaz10cnVl&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=320d-21&amp;linkId=91128851b475941698cadf499e9312d3&amp;language=en_GB&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(108, 184, 58) !important;\">Hyundai petrol tiller</a>&nbsp;is perfect for heavy duty landscaping and turfing projects.&nbsp;</font></div>');
