(1015, 'Maxine Rivera', 'teacher', 4, 867, '+61491170156', 'maxine-rivera@kemecademy.com', 'Professional internal design trainer', '$2y$10$fiEgjabGSso1ZuBX/NWAIeNbTmx989MuY5Yt2CGu472l6lqXSUIYG', NULL, NULL, '08Q2qeVTzOpjTVEB8049YO4Te8oUleVb0q6tw7zwW264T4gcOszcc1E0deMn', 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 1, NULL, '/store/1/posts/maxine.png', NULL, '/store/1/posts/cover2.jpg', NULL, 'Maxine Rivera is a seasoned professional trainer specializing in real estate renovation and home improvement. With over 15 years of experience in the industry, Maxine has successfully trained countless professionals in mastering the art of transforming properties into stunning living spaces.\r\n\r\nAs a certified expert in real estate renovation, Maxine possesses an extensive knowledge of construction techniques, design principles, and market trends. Her deep understanding of the industry allows her to guide professionals through every stage of the renovation process, from initial planning to project completion.\r\n\r\nMaxine\'s training sessions are renowned for their practicality and effectiveness. She combines her technical expertise with a hands-on approach, providing participants with real-life examples, case studies, and interactive exercises. Her ability to break down complex concepts into easily understandable steps empowers professionals to implement innovative solutions and achieve remarkable results.\r\n\r\nIn addition to her training expertise, Maxine is also a sought-after consultant for real estate developers and homeowners alike. She has collaborated on numerous high-profile renovation projects, offering her invaluable insights and strategic recommendations to ensure maximum return on investment.\r\n\r\nMaxine\'s passion for transforming properties and enhancing communities is evident in her commitment to helping professionals succeed in the real estate renovation industry. Through her engaging training programs, she equips participants with the skills, knowledge, and confidence necessary to excel in this competitive field.\r\n\r\nIf you\'re looking to sharpen your skills, expand your expertise, and stay ahead of the game in the realm of real estate renovation and home improvement, Maxine Rivera is the trainer you need. Join her transformative training sessions and unlock your true potential in the world of property renovation.', 'Al Wakrah ,27904 Hilpert Knoll', 18, 46, 49, 55, 0x0000000001010000007a87fa84a95b4440f17007d9bc8052c0, b'110', 'all', 'active', 1, 0, 'EN', NULL, 'America/New_York', 0, 0, '/store/1015/passport.jpg', '/store/1015/certificate_validation.jpg', NULL, 1, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 1624817207, NULL, NULL),
(1016, 'Roberto Dallas', 'teacher', 4, NULL, '+12025250175', 'robertodallas@hotmail.com', 'Home builder trainer', '$2y$10$9X4VL8jFciZVMfDZRvR2xeNLHyHgoXJ7B5kcHC030wvZJxH011HFm', NULL, NULL, '3SSEEBVSeHIrT9k5Lln1tV2cjle70YHYu7BWQ12oicCKvuDyK3Aa6ZUq3dE3', 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, NULL, '/store/1/robert.png', NULL, '/store/1/posts/roberto-cover.png', NULL, 'American Home Improvement, Inc. -  it is our mission to provide the highest quality of service in all aspects of our business. We are extremely thorough in the services that we provide and aim to be very receptive to any client\'s issues, questions or concerns and handle them promptly and professionally. We take the necessary steps to ensure that our clients are completely satisfied with all of our contractual and assumed responsibilities. Above all else, we will fulfill these responsibilities while maintaining the highest ethical standards in both our work and our character.\r\n\r\nGeneral Contracting: $15,000 to $1,000,000\r\nKitchen Remodeling: $30,000 to $300,000\r\nBathroom Remodeling: $18,000 to $150,000\r\nHome Additions: $100,000 to $1,000,000\r\nCustom Cabinets: $20,000 to $150,000\r\nKitchen/Bath Design: $10,000 to $150,000\r\nPlans and Design: $10,000 to $100,000\r\nSolar Installation: $10,000 to $100,000\r\n\r\nEstimates based on experience. Your actual costs may vary. Please contact us for a design consultation about your upcoming renovation.\r\n\r\nServices Provided\r\nBathroom Remodeling, General Contracting, Home Additions, Home Remodeling, Kitchen Remodeling, Outdoor Kitchen Construction, Cabinet Installation, Custom Cabinets, Outdoor Kitchen Design, Remodeling, Solar Installation, Kitchen Design, Bathroom Design, Plans and Designs, Complete Renovations, Home Renovations, Multiple Room Remodeling, Bedroom Renovation, Bathroom Renovation, Kitchen Renovation, Kitchen Layout Change, Bathroom Layout Change, Shower Renovation, Kitchen Construction, Bathroom Construction\r\n\r\nAreas Served\r\nAgoura, Agoura 