uN1lid0VDZDRrTlZRd3JzdV9MMkl2MGdPWHQxY1RMZmowM2x5WTVYV3FrdFJpXzZmd2pBMGt1M0xfWnJqT1FuOGd2eXVVMGxuMS1QeHkwdFNtcHl5d1FxZlNUZmhrZ09MbU9VcURRU05wWQ&q=https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F3rsw5U7&v=WrrTUSxxsxE\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-decoration: var(--yt-endpoint-text-regular-decoration,none); background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); display: var(--yt-endpoint-display,inline-block); cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: var(--yt-endpoint-word-wrap,none); word-break: var(--yt-endpoint-word-break,none); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\">https://amzn.to/3rsw5U7</a><span dir=\"auto\" class=\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(3, 3, 3); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\">\r\n\r\n</span><a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/hashtag/diycrew\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-decoration: var(--yt-endpoint-text-regular-decoration,none); background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); display: var(--yt-endpoint-display,inline-block); cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: var(--yt-endpoint-word-wrap,none); word-break: var(--yt-endpoint-word-break,none); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\">#diycrew</a><span dir=\"auto\" class=\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(3, 3, 3); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/hashtag/hrvdiy\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-decoration: var(--yt-endpoint-text-regular-decoration,none); background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); display: var(--yt-endpoint-display,inline-block); cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: var(--yt-endpoint-word-wrap,none); word-break: var(--yt-endpoint-word-break,none); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\">#hrvdiy</a><span dir=\"auto\" class=\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(3, 3, 3); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/hashtag/renovision\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-decoration: var(--yt-endpoint-text-regular-decoration,none); background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); display: var(--yt-endpoint-display,inline-block); cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: var(--yt-endpoint-word-wrap,none); word-break: var(--yt-endpoint-word-break,none); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\">#renovision</a><span dir=\"auto\" class=\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(3, 3, 3); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\">\r\n\r\nThe first step to any painting project is preparation. having a good sanding and priming job is the beat way to guarantee you will be happy with the finished ceiling.\r\n\r\nIn order to apply primer you must remember to apply pressure in order to push the paint into the drywall and then lightly back roll to remove extra paint from the surface.\r\n\r\nAfter you have primed I always suggest you sand with a 220 grit sandpaper to ensure any defects have been removed. \r\n\r\nThe secret to a great ceiling painting job is to paint the first and second coats in opposite directions. This will enable you to have perfect paint coverage and to finish rolling in the same direction as the sun coming into the room.\r\n\r\nAlways do a light sanding in between every coat of paint. On a ceiling I suggest using a flat paint with no acrylic additive. This gives you great coverage and reduces the chance of seeing the paint lines after you are done. It also helps you do touch up work without seeing the new work. \r\n\r\nWhen painting a ceiling always remember to use a long painting pole and keep your hands below your heart. This will help fight against fatigue and make the job much easier.\r\n\r\nThe secret to a perfect ceiling paint finish is to cut and roll while keeping the leading edge of the paint wet so that everything can melt together.\r\n\r\nNeed Answers or Advice for your DIY Project?\r\nBECOME A DIY MEMBER NOW!\r\n\r\nBecome a DIY Member by clicking the “join” button beside the “subscribe” button - </span><a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/HomeRenoVisionDIY/membership\" rel=\"nofollow\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-decoration: var(--yt-endpoint-text-regular-decoration,none); background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); display: var(--yt-endpoint-display,inline-block); cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: var(--yt-endpoint-word-wrap,none); word-break: var(--yt-endpoint-word-break,none); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\">https://www.youtube.com/c/HomeRenoVis...</a><span dir=\"auto\" class=\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(3, 3, 3); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\">\r\n► Get FULL access to me and my team for Q and A’s in the DIY Crew Forum\r\n► Participate in monthly LIVE streams for live consulting and Member support!\r\n\r\nShop Jeff’s favorite tools and great products and help support our next project!\r\n\r\n► Shop Wayfair 🇨🇦: </span><a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" spellcheck=\"false\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description&redir_token=QUFFLUhqbXJRNC1iMS0zd2RGejBrLXJycnVWN3JjNlhjUXxBQ3Jtc0ttSzhsZzIzQkJvZEUteVA5cWZ3eW9BaEdGQW5rXzVvSlVNUnVzUzBrbkNnckVoa1VNT3duc2pydHFLNWxYYW5ZSzA3Y3BDd2d4Tmw4M1RfX1B3MjZhMHlra3pkTm01REI